headline: Williams-Sonoma (NYSE:WSM) Slips 13% Over The Last Week
summary: Williams-Sonoma (NYSE:WSM) recently expanded its collaboration with AERIN, enriching its collection with luxury homeware items. Despite this positive development and strong fourth-quarter results, the stock experienced a 13% decline over the past week. This performance mirrors broader market trends, as the Dow faced substantial pressure due to issues such as UnitedHealth's forecast cut and heightened trade tensions impacting technology stocks.
